{"tid":1900381,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先算違反商品說明條例","createTime":"2020-02-27T07:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T22:22:58.000Z","uid":311306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35a812ad8cb7f95e9e2f24ac9565bec93f9f1f91","tid":1900381,"uid":311306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"小妹想問下如果有公司係購買服務同埋單據無寫明要比全數先可以refund, 依家想退款但係唔退得因為未俾全數, 算唔算誤導性遺漏?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c285c8d447640e85a4b0805207bded4a8cce3e5","tid":1900381,"uid":236410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35a812ad8cb7f95e9e2f24ac9565bec93f9f1f91","tid":1900381,"uid":311306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"小妹想問下如果有公司係購買服務同埋單據無寫明要比全數先可以refund, 依家想退款但係唔退得因為未俾全數, 算唔算誤導性遺漏?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T22:22:58.000Z","msg":"視乎：<br />\n-合約內容<br />\n-合約雙方行為<br />\n-賣家提供的貨物或服務是否乎合合約要求<br />\n<br />\n如果合約冇寫明，而佢提供嘅服務又達到合約要求，未必有得退款<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 誤導性遺漏只應用係消費者合約"}]}